safepasswords (1.0.1.0~noble) noble; urgency=high

  * Allow for a --salt command line option.
  * Allow for a --password command line option (to force the password).
  * Call strcasecmp() directly because our build system fails otherwise.
  * Moved debian/compat version to debian/control dependencies.
  * Fixed some documentation.

 -- Alexis Wilke <alexis@m2osw.com>  Fri, 26 Jan 2024 21:34:55 -0800

